---
import { useTranslation } from '../i18n/ui';

interface Props {
  lang: 'en' | 'es' | 'fr' | 'jp';
}

const { lang } = Astro.props;
const t = useTranslation(lang);

---

<main class="w-full min-h-screen bg-black text-white font-vanter-code">
  
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto border-x border-zinc-900 min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <div class="w-full border-b border-zinc-900 h-24 md:h-32"></div>

    <header class="w-full border-b border-zinc-900 py-20 md:py-28 px-6 flex justify-center items-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white text-center">
        Cookie Policy
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="w-full border-b border-zinc-900 py-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-500">Last Updated April 14, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 w-full flex justify-center">
      
      <article class="p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 w-full max-w-4xl flex justify-center">
        
        <div class="prose prose-invert w-full max-w-3xl
                    prose-headings:text-white prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:tracking-wide
                    prose-h2:text-2xl md:prose-h2:text-3xl prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:mb-6 first:prose-h2:mt-0
                    prose-p:text-zinc-400 prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-p:text-base
                    prose-li:text-zinc-400 prose-ul:list-disc
                    prose-strong:text-zinc-200
                    prose-a:text-white hover:prose-a:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">
          
          <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
          <p>This Cookie Policy explains how <strong>Vanter</strong> uses cookies and similar tracking technologies when you visit our website or use our software as a service (SaaS) platforms. Cookies are small text files that are stored on your browser or device by websites, apps, online media, and advertisements to remember your browser or device during and across website visits.</p>

          <h2>2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use cookies to ensure our platform functions properly, to understand how you interact with our services, and to improve your overall experience. Because we provide software architectures and client portals, some cookies are strictly necessary for security and authentication purposes.</p>

          <h2>3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Strictly Necessary Cookies:</strong> These are essential for you to browse our website and use its features, such as accessing secure areas of our SaaS platforms. Without these cookies, services like user authentication and session management cannot be provided.</li>
            <li><strong>Preference Cookies:</strong> These cookies allow our website to remember choices you make, such as your preferred language (e.g., English, Spanish, French, or Japanese) or the region you are in, providing a more personalized experience.</li>
            <li><strong>Performance and Analytics Cookies:</strong> We use these to collect information about how visitors use our website, such as which pages are visited most often and if they receive error messages. These cookies do not collect information that individually identifies a visitor; all data is aggregated and anonymous.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p>In addition to our own cookies, we may also use various trusted third-party plug-ins and tools (such as analytics providers or cloud infrastructure monitors) to report usage statistics and improve platform performance. These third parties may set their own cookies on your device when you interact with our services.</p>

          <h2>5. Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h2>
          <p>Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings preferences. You can configure your browser to accept all cookies, reject all cookies, or notify you when a cookie is set. Please note that if you choose to disable strictly necessary cookies, certain core functionalities of our SaaS platform (like logging into your account) may not function correctly.</p>

          <h2>6. Changes to This Cookie Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any material changes by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy.</p>

          <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions about our use of cookies or other technologies, please contact us at <strong></strong>info@vanter.net</p>

        </div>

      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</main>